  "title": "6723 - Service Engineer [Jurong East | Fire Protection | up to $4k]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Service Engineer</strong></p><p>Salary: $ 3000 - $ 4000<br />Working Hours & Days: Monday – Friday, 9 am – 6 pm<br />Address: Jurong East</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee and coordinate fire protection system installations across designated sites</li><li>Assist operation manager in planning, scheduling, and site execution activities</li><li>Liaise with clients, consultants, subcontractors, and authorities on project matters</li><li>Ensure site works comply with safety regulations, project timelines, and fire codes</li><li>Review technical drawings, monitor material delivery, and prepare project documentation</li><li>Review and align Fire protection design drawings to ensure compliance with design specifications and guidelines (Sprinkler System, Fire Alarm System, Hosereel System, Wet / Dry riser system, Fire Hydrant System, Fire man intercom system)</li><li>To attend meeting with contractors to address issues and update progress</li><li>To lead tender preparation and execution thru tenderboard</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in M & E Engineering field will be preferable</li><li>Relevant working experience in Fire Protection</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>📲Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han) 📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-senior-hr-executive-education-sector-marine-parade-35k%E2%80%934k-hr-lifecycle-er-supreme-hr-advisory-f4d18bea51dfbe07dff1bccc5ef1e127/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p>",
